#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-secondary o_translate_inline\">Explore our "
"services</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-secondary o_translate_inline\">Découvrez nos "
"services</a>"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_cover
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-2\">ESTATE ®</font><br/>Your easy home search, "
"all in one"
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-2\">ESTATE ®</font><br/>Une recherche de logement "
"facile et tout-en-un"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"Amazing team! smiling, always nice to talk with, they always have the best "
"advices for you, adapted to your needs!"
msgstr ""
"Une équipe formidable ! Souriante, toujours agréable à parler, ils vous "
"donnent les meilleurs conseils, adaptés à vos besoins !"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_text_image
msgid "Are you thinking of selling?"
msgstr "Vous envisagez de vendre ?"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid "Bored with your interior?"
msgstr "Vous en avez assez de votre intérieur ?"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "Carefully handpicked by our experts"
msgstr "Sélectionnés avec soin par nos experts"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Customer, bought a house"
msgstr "Client, a acheté une maison"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Customer, bought an appartement"
msgstr "Client, a acheté un appartement"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Customer, sold an appartement"
msgstr "Client, a vendu un appartement"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "Discover our latest properties"
msgstr "Découvrez nos dernières acquisitions"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid ""
"Discover our tailor-made services to embellish the decoration of your home."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez nos services sur mesure pour embellir la décoration de votre "
"maison."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_real_estate.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom d'affichage"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Elegant, modern sophisticated architecture with an impressive in large scale "
"home designed with the finest imported finishes. Marble and wood floors..."
msgstr ""
"Une architecture élégante, moderne et sophistiquée avec une impressionnante "
"maison à grande échelle conçue avec les finitions importées les plus "
"raffinées. Du marbre et des planchers en bois..."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"From start to finish, they were extremely professional, friendly, helpful "
"and easy to do business with. Very happy with the experience and the company."
msgstr ""
"Du début à la fin, ils ont été extrêmement professionnels, sympathiques, "
"serviables et il a été facile de faire des affaires avec eux. Je suis très "
"satisfait de l'expérience et de l'entreprise."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "House On The Hill"
msgstr "La maison sur la colline"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_real_estate.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_text_image
msgid ""
"Make an appointment for a free valuation of your property. We visit the "
"property, advise you on a realistic asking price and we explain our way of "
"working. <br/>\n"
"        You can decide in all freedom whether or not you would like to work "
"with us for the sale of your property."
msgstr ""
"Prenez rendez-vous pour une évaluation gratuite de votre bien. Nous visitons "
"le bien, nous vous conseillons sur un prix de vente réaliste et nous vous "
"expliquons notre méthode de travail. <br/>\n"
"Vous pouvez décider en toute liberté si vous souhaitez ou non travailler "
"avec nous pour la vente de votre bien."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "Moutain View"
msgstr "Vue montagne"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid ""
"Our decoration experts are at your disposal to guide you step by step in the "
"design of your interior and will give you the best advice for your interior "
"design."
msgstr ""
"Nos experts en décoration sont à votre disposition pour vous guider pas à "
"pas dans l'aménagement de votre intérieur et vous donner les meilleurs "
"conseils pour votre décoration d'intérieur."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "Paradise Residence"
msgstr "Résidence Paradis"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"Positive energy, great team spirit, hard workers and awesome people! I "
"warmly recommend them!"
msgstr ""
"Une énergie positive, un grand esprit d'équipe, des travailleurs acharnés et "
"des gens formidables ! Je les recommande vivement !"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_cover
msgid "Search Now"
msgstr "Rechercher maintenant"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"The house is surrounded by garden terraces that create an intimate ambience. "
"With no overlooking neighbours, the garden offers real privacy."
msgstr ""
"La maison est entourée de terrasses qui créent une ambiance intime. Sans vis-"
"à-vis, le jardin offre une réelle intimité."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_real_estate.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thèmes utiles"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "View details"
msgstr "Voir les détails"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_call_to_action
msgid "Want To Become A Real Estate Agent?"
msgstr "Vous voulez devenir agent immobilier ?"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Waste no time in viewing this truly stunning property. The property's "
"surroundings really set it apart, offering idyllic sea views overlooking a "
"park."
msgstr ""
"Ne perdez pas de temps à visiter cette superbe propriété. Les environs de la "
"propriété la distinguent vraiment, offrant des vues idylliques sur la mer et "
"sur un parc."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_call_to_action
msgid "We'll help you to grow your career and growth."
msgstr "Nous vous aiderons à développer votre carrière et votre croissance."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_title
msgid "Where every house becomes a home."
msgstr "Nous faisons de chaque maison un foyer."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_cover
msgid ""
"With a simple click, finding your dream home has never been easier.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"Il suffit d'un simple clic pour trouver la maison de vos rêves.<br/><br/>"
